OL,3,CEnergy bills set to fall as Tories and
OL,4,CLabour clash over policy
OL,6,FThe regulator announced it is dropping
OL,7,Fits price cap from the current #1,690
OL,8,Ffor a typical dual fuel household in
OL,9,FEngland, Scotland and Wales to #1,568,
OL,10,Fa drop of #122 over the course of a
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FThis is around #500 less than the cap
OL,14,Fin July last year, when it was #2,074.
OL,16,FOfgem changes the price cap every
OL,17,Fthree months based on several factors,
OL,18,Fthe most important of which is the
OL,19,Fprice of energy on wholesale markets.
