OL,3,CEnergy bills set to fall as Tories and
OL,4,CLabour clash over policy
OL,6,FDespite the decrease, Labour pointed
OL,7,Fout it would still be #400 more than
OL,8,Fin 2021.
OL,10,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer is
OL,11,Fusing a visit to Scotland to promote
OL,12,Fhis plan for a publicly-owned green
OL,13,Felectricity generator, which he said
OL,14,Fwould cut bills and boost energy
OL,15,Fsecurity.
OL,17,FSir Keir is set to say that "after 14
OL,18,Fyears of Tory chaos" people "are
OL,19,Fdesperate for change".
