OL,3,CEnergy bills set to fall as Tories and
OL,4,CLabour clash over policy
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, Ofgem chief executive
OL,7,FJonathan Brearley told the Energy
OL,8,FSecurity and Net Zero Committee that
OL,9,Fprices "are still significantly higher
OL,10,Fthan they were before, and when we
OL,11,Flook further out our best estimate is
OL,12,Fthat prices are going to stay high and
OL,13,Fvolatile over time".
OL,15,FOfgem is currently reviewing the price
OL,16,Fcap and looking at how it is
OL,17,Fcalculated.
